title: Scary Kids Scaring Kids - Complete Discography - 2003-2010
description:
Complete collection of one of my favorite bands, Scary Kids Scaring Kids. Includes all studio albums, with unreleased demos, singles, and rare songs. 

(2003) After Dark EP (Original Self Released Demos)
(2003) Interscope Records Demos
(2005) After Dark (FLAC)
(2005) After Dark (Reissue/Remastered)
(2005) The City Sleeps In Flames
(2005) The City Sleeps In Flames (FLAC)
(2005) The Only Medicine - Promotional Single
(2005) The Only Medicine - Promotional Single (Lossless)
(2006) A Santa Cause It's a Punk Rock Christmas (Single)
(2007) Faces - Single
(2007) Scary Kids Scaring Kids - Self Titled
(2007) Scary Kids Scaring Kids - Self Titled (FLAC)
(2007) Scary Kids Scaring Kids - Self Titled (Instrumentals)
(2007) Snake Devil - Single (iTunes)
(2007) The Deep End - Single

(2013) Coma Prevail Demos (Tyson Stevens old band and last songs featuring his vocals before he passed)
(2017) After Dark Vinyl Reissue (Includes unreleased song)

Please seed and enjoy
